# Draft:Georgie Sicking

Georgie Sicking (May 20, 1921 - November 6, 2016) was an American rancher and poet.
Life
Georgie Connell Sicking was born on May 20, 1921 in Seligman, Arizona.
Awards and honors
She was inducted into the Cowgirl Hall of Fame.
Winner of the Gail Garner award for Outstanding Working Cowboy Poet.
